title: MisterMusic Show 300 new indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show episode 300 (192 kbps MP3 stereo) [2 hours]

Woah..It's my 300th show!

New music on this week's show from Jimi Goodwin, Wye Oak, The Pains of Being Pure At Heart, and another new track from the latest album by The Mary Onettes.
The 'Oldie of the Week' is a huge smash rock n' roll hit that was number 1, in 1982 during the entire month of April.

Plus a really eclectic mix of stuff this week.... check it out.


The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
